description: The insatiable craving for Misha’s cupcakes has burst beyond their 6 storefront locations, and now Misha’s Cupcakes truck is taking these tasty baked treats throughout the streets of Miami!You’ll find fantastic flavors like Chocolate, Cookie Dough, Peanut Butter, and Oreo, and new favorites like Guava with Cream Cheese, Cherry Pistachio, and Kahlua, to name a few. And if you need delicious cupcakes at your next event, be sure to invite Misha’s and they will make your party sweetly complete.
name: Misha's Cupcakes
